From: HyprWM Fedora maintainers
Date: Wed, 15 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] cmake: preserve distribution compiler flags

Do not append an optimization level after the flags supplied by the RPM
build system.
---
 CMakeLists.txt | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/CMakeLists.txt b/CMakeLists.txt
index 32a4138..7e232b7 100644
--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -48,7 +48,6 @@ if(CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE MATCHES Debug OR CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE MATCHES DEBUG)
   message(STATUS "Configuring hyprlauncher in Debug")
   add_compile_definitions(HYPRLAUNCHER_DEBUG)
 else()
-  add_compile_options(-O3)
   message(STATUS "Configuring hyprlauncher in Release")
 endif()
 
